{"tid":2326420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法院排期趕不及16歲生日前處理 少年認暴動罪不能於少年庭處理","createTime":"2020-12-15T10:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:23:12.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f0c577923ba2f71f73547a9d503d20f6b29c54","tid":2326420,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"去年11月中市民持續發動「三罷」堵路示威，發展成理大激烈衝突，其間多人被捕。有15歲男學生及年輕地盤男工被指在旺角蒙面參與暴動，男生更被指縱火及管有一個士巴拿。兩人遭控暴動、非法集結時使用蒙面物品等罪，今日在區域法院提堂時，15歲被告透露將會認罪，代表大狀申請將被告轉介到少年庭判刑，惟<span class=\"red\">因法院最快亦只能排期至明年1月中處理少年的案件，屆時少年已年屆16歲，不符少年庭處理的資格，少年最終只能維持於區域法院判刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n辯方指希望可判處非監禁式刑罰，高官明言沒法可在被告生日前處理， 區域法院法官有酌情權，判處少年法庭的判刑選擇 ，又指同類案件上訴庭已經有清晰的指引，「你都見到近來的判例係點樣架啦？」最終案件維持在區域法院處理，<span class=\"red\">15歲被告將於明年2月10日正式答辯。</span>"},{"pid":"37caa95cf10dac237473d73795d729f9321c95d9","tid":2326420,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=5a35bae8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA%2F&h=f1c85a8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA/</a>"},{"pid":"ebc2b47c7cb0a35b1ce782d60b29a477d18c6a75","tid":2326420,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43f3c17f44c0c974c9778e91cc48d426f11d357d","tid":2326420,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係睇案發時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217e89b156b4a78ae655778e82c806d3c9605429","tid":2326420,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT